    <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <h2>What our happy customers say</h2>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 border-top"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <div class="strong-view strong-view-id-1 default wpmtst-default slider-container slider-mode-fade slider-adaptive controls-style-buttons nav-position-inside" data-count="5" data-slider-var="strong_slider_id_1" data-state="idle"><div class="strong-content wpmslider-content"><div class="wpmtst-testimonial testimonial t-slide post-3344"><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-inner testimonial-inner"><h3 class="wpmtst-testimonial-heading testimonial-heading">MAIAN T.</h3><div data-infinite-loop="false" class="wpmtst-testimonial-content testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>My poor car baby looked like Zeus dropped a bag of marbles on her before I took it into Front Range Dent Removal. I chose them based on the positive reviews and can echo everyone else’s sentiments about their excellent customer service.</p></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-field testimonial-field testimonial-name"><span class="strong-rating-wrapper in-view"><span class="strong-rating"><span class="star" style="display: none;"></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span></span></span></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial testimonial t-slide post-3345"><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-inner testimonial-inner"><h3 class="wpmtst-testimonial-heading testimonial-heading">TYLER D.</h3><div data-infinite-loop="false" class="wpmtst-testimonial-content testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>All I can say is that I wish I took a before photo, because the dent in question is now non-existent! Great customer service, fair price for the quality of work and great workmanship. I’ll definitely return to get some trunk dents out of my 2015 mustang.</p></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-field testimonial-field testimonial-name"><span class="strong-rating-wrapper in-view"><span class="strong-rating"><span class="star" style="display: none;"></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span></span></span></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial testimonial t-slide post-3354"><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-inner testimonial-inner"><h3 class="wpmtst-testimonial-heading testimonial-heading">BECKY R.</h3><div data-infinite-loop="false" class="wpmtst-testimonial-content testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>I took my pretty severely-damaged car here after the first vicious hail storm this past spring, and they did an amazing job on my car. They removed all the dents from the body perfectly and ordered a couple trim parts (that are metal and not fixable, just easily replaceable), &#8230;</p></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-field testimonial-field testimonial-name"><span class="strong-rating-wrapper in-view"><span class="strong-rating"><span class="star" style="display: none;"></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span></span></span></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial testimonial t-slide post-3355"><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-inner testimonial-inner"><h3 class="wpmtst-testimonial-heading testimonial-heading">PAUL P.</h3><div data-infinite-loop="false" class="wpmtst-testimonial-content testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>Phenomenal service and terrific outcome- total cost was 1/3 of what body shop would have charged to repair/ paint and looks good as new. Anson also went out of his way to accommodate us and went above and beyond in completing the work and ensuring we were completely &#8230;</p></div><div class="wpmtst-testimonial-field testimonial-field testimonial-name"><span class="strong-rating-wrapper in-view"><span class="strong-rating"><span class="star" style="display: none;"></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46.4-33.7l-25-145.5 105.7-103c19-18.5 8.5-50.8-17.7-54.6L382 150.2 316.7 17.8c-11.7-23.6-45.6-23.9-57.4 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="star" style="display: inline-block;"><svg class="star_solid" aria-hidden="true" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="-8 -8 584 520"><path d="M259.3 17.8L194 150.2 47.9 171.5c-26.2 3.8-36.7 36.1-17.7 54.6l105.7 103-25 145.5c-4.5 26.3 23.2 46 46.4 33.7L288 439.6l130.7 68.7c23.2 12.2 50.9-7.4 46